criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age >18

          -  Non-small cell lung cancer stage I to II, justifying resection major pulmonary by VATS
             or RATS

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Partial or total amputation localized to the lower limb;

          -  Weight greater than 100 kg;

          -  Orthopedic, vascular or neurological disorders leading to the incapacity of realize
             the TS6M;

          -  Patient under tutorship or curatorship;

          -  Pregnant woman.
